<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><b><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; color: black;">Description<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><b><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">CORIA 2008 est la cinqui&egrave;me
&eacute;dition de <st1:PersonName productid="la Conf&#65513;rence" w:st="on">la
Conf&eacute;rence</st1:PersonName>
en Recherche d&#8217;Information et Applications. Organis&eacute;e avec le support
de l'ARIA
(Association francophone de Recherche d'Information et Applications),
CORIA est
le point de rassemblement de la communaut&eacute; francophone en recherche
d&#8217;information et constitue un lieu de rencontre privil&eacute;gi&eacute; pour les
chercheurs du
domaine. Elle se veut largement ouverte &agrave; l&#8217;ensemble de la communaut&eacute;
scientifique
concern&eacute;e par cette th&eacute;matique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">La conf&eacute;rence donne aux participants
le moyen de faire partager leurs travaux sur les fondements th&eacute;oriques
et pratiques
du domaine. La recherche d&#8217;information conna&icirc;t une &eacute;volution sans
pr&eacute;c&eacute;dent
avec en particulier la croissance des applications li&eacute;es au Web. Les
travaux
sont extr&ecirc;mement vari&eacute;s, allant des mod&egrave;les th&eacute;oriques &agrave; la recherche
dans des
domaines sp&eacute;cialis&eacute;s sur le web, en passant par les interfaces
homme-machine intelligentes,
la recherche de documents multilingues ou multim&eacute;dia, les biblioth&egrave;ques
&eacute;lectroniques.
Le domaine est lui m&ecirc;me en pleine mutation et s&#8217;ouvre en permanence &agrave;
de
nouvelles th&eacute;matiques&nbsp;: recherche web; applications Web2.0 avec
l&#8217;exploitation
des r&eacute;seaux sociaux; recherche dans les blogs, forums et autres sites
communautaires; analyse des grands graphes du web; analyse de rumeurs,
de sentiments,
etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">Le public vis&eacute; par CORIA 2008
est celui des chercheurs d&eacute;butants et confirm&eacute;s effectuant leur
recherche dans
le domaine de la Recherche d&#8217;Information ou dans des domaines connexes,
en
France ou dans des pays francophones comme ceux d&#8217;Afrique du Nord, la
Suisse,
la Belgique et le Canada.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">***************************************************************************<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><b style=""><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; color: black;">Th&eacute;matiques<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="font-size: 14pt; color: black;">De fa&ccedil;on non limitative, CORIA
sollicite des communications sur les th&eacute;matiques
suivantes<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><b><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Th&eacute;orie
et mod&egrave;les formels pour <st1:PersonName productid="la RI" w:st="on">la
RI</st1:PersonName>&nbsp;:
</span><span style="color: black;">mod&egrave;le logique, mod&egrave;les de langages,
mod&egrave;les
probabilistes.<span style=""><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">RI
multilingue, traduction.</span><span style="color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Multim&eacute;dia
: </span><span style="color: black;">image, audio, vid&eacute;os, son,
musique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Classification,
clustering, ranking, apprentissage automatique&nbsp;:
filtrage, spam, TDT, ranking pour les moteurs de recherche.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Traitement
Automatique de <st1:PersonName productid="la Langue Naturelle"
 w:st="on">la Langue Naturelle</st1:PersonName> pour <st1:PersonName
 productid="la RI" w:st="on">la RI</st1:PersonName> :</span><span
 style="color: black;"> Questions
R&eacute;ponses, extraction d&#8217;information, acquisition lexicale.<span style=""><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">RI Web&nbsp;:
passage &agrave; l&#8217;&eacute;chelle, grands graphes,
utilisation de la topologie du web, lois de puissances, citations,
analyse de
liens.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">R&eacute;seaux
sociaux&nbsp;: analyse de blogs et de sites communautaires, suivi de
conversation, analyse de rumeur, analyse de sentiments.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Recherche
collaborative&nbsp;: filtrage, syst&egrave;mes de recommandation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Interaction
utilisateur&nbsp;: interrogation flexible,
interfaces, visualisation, mod&eacute;lisation de l&#8217;utilisateur, tests
d&#8217;usage,
visualisation de gros corpus.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Traitement
et repr&eacute;sentation des connaissances&nbsp;: m&eacute;ta
donn&eacute;es, ontologies, web s&eacute;mantique, ing&eacute;nierie des connaissances.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Biblioth&egrave;ques
num&eacute;riques.</span><span style="color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Syst&egrave;mes
de RI d&eacute;di&eacute;s : </span><span style="color: black;">recherche
d'information
g&eacute;nomique, g&eacute;ographique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">RI
distribu&eacute;e, P2P.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Outils
pour <st1:PersonName productid="la RI" w:st="on">la RI</st1:PersonName>
: </span><span style="color: black;">&eacute;valuation, bancs d&#8217;essais,
m&eacute;triques, exp&eacute;rimentations
qualitatives des syst&egrave;mes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="margin-left: 51.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -11.35pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
 style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; color: black;"><span style="">o<span
 style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="color: black;">Langages
de requ&ecirc;tes pour la recherche d&#8217;information.</span><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<div
 style="border-style: none none dotted; border-color: -moz-use-text-color -moz-use-text-color windowtext; border-width: medium medium 3pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 1pt;">
<p class="MsoNormal"
 style="border: medium none ; padding: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><b><span
 style="font-size: 16pt; color: black;">Consignes
aux auteurs<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">Les auteurs doivent d&#8217;abord
d&eacute;poser un <b>r&eacute;sum&eacute;</b> pour le </span><span class="moz-txt-tag"><b
 style="">3 d&eacute;cembre 2007</b></span><span style="">, p</span><span
 style="color: black;">uis
d&eacute;poser leur <b>article</b> pour le </span><span class="moz-txt-tag"><b
 style="">10 d&eacute;cembre 2007</b></span><span style=""><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">Les soumissions peuvent &ecirc;tre
faites en anglais ou en fran&ccedil;ais. Les contributions peuvent concerner
des
travaux acad&eacute;miques ou des applications industrielles.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">Les textes des communications
doivent comporter 16 pages maximum au format des revues Hermes. Ils
doivent
&ecirc;tre pr&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;s d&#8217;une page de garde comportant&nbsp;le titre, les noms et
coordonn&eacute;es pr&eacute;cises des auteurs, une liste de mots cl&eacute;s en Fran&ccedil;ais et
en
Anglais, un r&eacute;sum&eacute; d&#8217;une dizaine de lignes au maximum. La mention
&laquo;&nbsp;application industrielle&nbsp;&raquo; doit &ecirc;tre port&eacute;e sur la page de garde le
cas &eacute;ch&eacute;ant.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="color: black;">Les articles peuvent &ecirc;tre &eacute;crits
en Word ou en Latex. Le format des articles Word et Latex peut &ecirc;tre
t&eacute;l&eacute;charg&eacute; &agrave;
l&#8217;adresse suivante&nbsp;: <a
 href="http://www.hermes-science.fr/fr/cons_revues.html">http://www.hermes-science.fr/fr/cons_revues.html</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<pre style="text-align: justify;"><span
 style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black;">Les articles, au format PDF exclusivement, sont &agrave; d&eacute;poser sur le site</span><span
 style="color: black;"> </span><a
 href="http://www.easychair.org/CORIA-2008/">http://www.easychair.org/CORIA-2008/</a></pre>
